Name: SI! Type ERR_a07 [Pub Edition]
Description:
EnemiesNoSync Edition, For Pubbing. REQUIRES CD2 B14+. Breaking the Limit in Send it! Type R. What is Elite Restriction Release? 90% of enemies have a chance to spawn in Elite variant, Elite enemies stats are tuned significantly, for Balance. New Elite variants are also borns with new quirks to ensure the enjoyment of the difficulty.
    Alpha 07:
  - Nitra Cost reverted from 40/50 back to 45.
  - Increase Cooldown of Elites once killed (United number across all difficulties), except Elite Breeder. 
  - Increase WaveSpawners Interval (Except SI! and MSX).
  - Reduce MaxSpawnCount of Elite Leeches and Elite Spitballer.
  - Reduce Elite Kursite Spitter damage dealt by ~7.5%.
